409
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,119
You did so good.

410
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:26,240
Uh, I mean, the match was cancelled
and we were losing anyway, but…

411
00:24:26,319 --> 00:24:27,440
Thanks.

412
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,400
So what's going on?

413
00:24:31,599 --> 00:24:32,799
[Imogen] I…

414
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,920
[boys shushing]

415
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:35,839
I…

416
00:24:37,799 --> 00:24:41,559
wanted to ask you if, um…

417
00:24:42,359 --> 00:24:44,720
Like, this is really random.
[laughs nervously]

418
00:24:45,559 --> 00:24:50,039
But maybe we could,
like… go out somewhere.

419
00:24:50,119 --> 00:24:51,799
-[students exclaiming]
-Together.

420
00:24:53,799 --> 00:24:56,119
Like, I guess sort of a… date.

421
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:58,559
Or something.

422
00:25:00,359 --> 00:25:01,359
Oh. Um…

423
00:25:02,559 --> 00:25:03,640
[Harry] Go on, Nick.

424
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:06,079
[all chuckling]

425
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:12,319
Yeah. I guess so, sure.

426
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,200
[Harry laughing] Yes, lad.

427
00:25:16,039 --> 00:25:17,519
Lads, let's get out of here.

428
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:20,960
[Imogen giggles]

429
00:25:29,799 --> 00:25:31,839
[peppy music playing]

